review.reviewBody: Yummy food and excellent customer service!

The Lhaksa brothis  not the best. Ive had better but the ingredients were great.i ordered veggies instead of noodles and all of the ingredients jncludng seafood tasted good.  The Roti Canai was good but the dippings  sauce was disappointing. The Pan Fried Eggplant & Green Bean with Laksa Paste was good.
Items are listed as vegan but contain shrimp and meat with no way to specify you actually want it vegan. Please fix this as it is false advertising right now which is not acceptable.
some of the chicken pieces weren't cooked properly
All excellent but the veggies if there was Brussels sprouts not bean sprouts I didn't see any abd well it was advertised as market fresh etc, again still good.
